  author = {Bahreini, Roya and Ahmadov, Ravan and McKeen, Stu A. and Vu, Kennedy T. and Dingle, Justin H. and Apel, Eric C. and Blake, Donald R. and Blake, Nicola and Campos, Teresa L. and Cantrell, Chris and Flocke, Frank and Fried, Alan and Gilman, Jessica B. and Hills, Alan J. and Hornbrook, Rebecca S. and Huey, Greg and Kaser, Lisa and Lerner, Brian M. and Mauldin, Roy L. and Meinardi, Simone and Montzka, Denise D. and Richter, Dirk and Schroeder, Jason R. and Stell, Meghan and Tanner, David and Walega, James and Weibring, Peter and Weinheimer, Andrew},
